title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week - Heliotropes record "Take It Out On Me"
description: This week's "Track of the Week" features the single "Take It Out On Me" from Converse Rubber Tracks recording artist Heliotropes. Watch as the band gets familiar with the Converse Rubber Tracks studio, plays around with the different recording set-ups and sound options and evaluate each recording to get the final version of their original single just right.
